OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780297676
OL,3,CWoman dead and man in critical
OL,4,Ccondition after attempting to rescue
OL,5,Cdog from sea
OL,7,FA woman has died and a man has been
OL,8,Fleft in a critical condition after
OL,9,Fgetting into difficulty in the sea.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to
OL,12,FFleetwood Beach in Thornton Cleveleys
OL,13,Fjust after 8pm on Saturday 30 May,
OL,14,Fafter receiving reports that two
OL,15,Fpeople had got into difficulty in the
OL,16,Fwater.
OL,18,FIt is understood the two people had
OL,19,Fgone into the water in an attempt to
OL,20,Frescue their dog, who had become stuck.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
