OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780297676
OL,3,CWoman dead and man in critical
OL,4,Ccondition after attempting to rescue
OL,5,Cdog from sea
OL,7,FHM Coastguard recovered a woman in her
OL,8,F60s and a man, also in his 60s, from
OL,9,Fthe water to be treated by paramedics.
OL,11,FThe woman was pronounced dead at the
OL,12,Fhospital, while the man remains in a
OL,13,Fcritical condition.
OL,15,FLancashire Police say enquiries to
OL,16,Fidentify her next of kin are ongoing.
OL,17,FThey added that the dog is safe and
OL,18,Fwell.
